{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"usefulItems":"baking paper","id":"r168164","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-voERnwOozTE\/XZapf9TT7zI\/AAAAAAAAhRU\/fejmE2ToVjoB2RU00GTEjAKcyknoTEVSQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_03PkPUk2lAnub5IX.png","title":"Carrot coriander soup and tikka salmon with steamed vegetables","publishedAt":"2018-10-15T00:00:00Z","ingredients":[{"content":"450 g carrots, 150 g cut into slices (approx. |5 mm) and 300 g cut into chunks"},{"content":"200 g broccoli florets"},{"content":"4 fresh salmon fillets (150-180 g each)"},{"content":"½ - 1 tsp salt, plus extra to taste"},{"content":"2 pinches freshly ground black pepper"},{"content":"4 tsp tikka paste"},{"content":"50 g red lentils"},{"content":"½ lemon, zest only"},{"content":"2 cm fresh ginger, sliced"},{"content":"100 g onions, cut into quarters"},{"content":"1 garlic clove"},{"content":"50 g butter, cut in pieces"},{"content":"700 g water"},{"content":"1 heaped tsp vegetable stock paste, homemade"},{"content":"2 sprigs fresh coriander, plus some extra leaves to garnish"},{"content":"100 g milk"},{"content":"4 tsp cream, to garnish (optional)"}],"nutrition":{"protein":"39.4 g","fat":"35 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"23 g","calories":"2360 kJ \/ 564 kcal"},"preparations":[{"content":"Weigh 150 g carrots slices and broccoli florets in Varoma dish."},{"content":"Insert Varoma tray in Varoma dish, line Varoma tray with baking paper and arrange salmon fillets on Varoma tray. Season with 1 pinch salt and ground pepper, spread 1 tsp tikka paste on top of each salmon fillet and set Varoma aside."},{"content":"Place lentils, lemon zest and ginger into mixing bowl, chop <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>."},{"content":"Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Chop again <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>."},{"content":"Add 300 g carrots chunks, onions, garlic, and butter, chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add water, stock paste, ½-1 tsp salt and 1 pinch pepper, place Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set covered Varoma aside on a plate to keep warm."},{"content":"Add coriander and milk and blend soup <b>1 min\/speed 5<b><strong>-10, increasing speed gradually<\/strong>. Serve the soup hot, garnished with some coriander leaves and a swirl of cream. Garnish the salmon tikka with remaining coriander leaves, finely cut, and serve with steamed vegetables on side."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Replace vegetables with any other vegetables of your choice that cook in the same time. Replace salmon with other fish fillets of your choice."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","4 portions"]}